---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";

const coffeeBeans = "/home/coffeeBeans.png";
---

<section
  id="historia"
  class="bg-cream-dark px-4 py-20 sm:px-6 sm:py-28 lg:px-8 lg:py-36 overflow-hidden"
>
  <div
    class="flex flex-col gap-14 items-center max-w-[1280px] mx-auto lg:flex-row lg:gap-24"
  >
    <!-- Text column -->
    <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col gap-8 relative z-10 reveal">
      <!-- Label -->
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
        <div class="w-12 h-px bg-green-cafe"></div>
        <span
          class="text-green-cafe text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase font-medium"
          >Nuestra Historia</span
        >
      </div>

      <h2
        class="font-display text-4xl font-normal leading-tight text-stone-cafe sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl text-balance"
      >
        Honrando la Tradición<br />de <span class="italic">Antioquia</span>
      </h2>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-stone-mid font-light sm:text-xl">
          En Raíces, creemos que el café es un hilo conductor entre el pasado y
          el presente. Nacimos con el propósito de exaltar la labor de los
          campesinos de Marinilla, llevando lo mejor de sus cosechas a tu taza.
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-stone-mid font-light sm:text-xl">
          Nuestro espacio está diseñado para que te sientas como en casa,
          rodeado de aromas que evocan recuerdos y sabores que despiertan los
          sentidos. Ven y sé parte de nuestra familia cafetera.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Accent badge -->
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-4 mt-2 p-5 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-cream-border max-w-md">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-green-cafe/10 flex items-center justify-center text-green-cafe">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z"></path>
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="font-display text-lg text-stone-cafe">Origen 100% Antioqueño</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-stone-mid font-light">Granos seleccionados de la región</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Image  -->
    <div class="flex-1 relative w-full max-w-2xl mx-auto lg:max-w-none group reveal reveal-delay-2">
      <div
        class="absolute -inset-4 bg-green-cafe/10 rounded-[2.5rem] rotate-3 -z-10 sm:-inset-6 transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:rotate-6 group-hover:bg-green-cafe/20"
      >
      </div>
      <div
        class="absolute -inset-4 bg-cream/50 rounded-[2.5rem] -rotate-2 -z-20 sm:-inset-6 transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:-rotate-4"
      >
      </div>
      <div class="relative z-10 p-3 bg-white rounded-[2.2rem] shadow-2xl">
        <Image
          src={coffeeBeans}
          alt="Granos de café en saco de fique"
          width={1920}
          height={1080}
          class="w-full h-[380px] object-cover rounded-[1.8rem] sm:h-[480px] lg:h-[620px] transform transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-[1.02]"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
